      "final_prompt": {
        "prompt": "Design a 3×3 grid poster for Xiaohongshu sleep wellness content, intended for 9-panel carousel posting with clean, premium, feminine lifestyle aesthetic.\n\nStyle/medium: editorial social media graphic design with the gentle warmth of a curated wellness journal, light skeuomorphic illustration, magazine-quality typography\nComposition: standard 3×3 grid layout with clear panel boundaries, each cell self-contained and centered, generous gutters between panels for clean slicing\nSubject: 9-panel sleep tips carousel — Panel 1 (cover): \"让你倒头就睡的8个 tips\" with subtitle \"失眠党、熬夜党一定要收藏\" + soft bed, moon, pillow, eye mask; Panels 2-8: numbered tips 1-8 with titles and body text as specified; Panel 9: tip 8 + \"收藏这组，今晚试试看\" footer\nScene/backdrop: cream white and oat base with soft gradients, each panel a serene vignette of bedroom and evening rituals\nLighting/mood: the quiet hush of a wind-down ritual, soft evening light settling like a warm blanket\nColor palette: cream white, soft beige, pale oat, light caramel with deep brown text accents — a palette that whispers rest\nMaterials/textures: matte paper warmth, soft fabric folds, ceramic smoothness, the gentle opacity of steamed milk\nText (verbatim): \n  让你倒头就睡的8个 tips\n  失眠党、熬夜党一定要收藏\n  1. 睡前1小时别玩手机\n  蓝光会让大脑更清醒，越刷越睡不着。\n  2. 睡前把灯光调暗\n  暖光环境能帮助身体进入\"准备睡觉\"的状态。\n  3. 房间温度别太高\n  稍微凉一点，更容易快速入睡。\n  4. 晚上别喝浓茶咖啡\n  咖啡因会延迟困意，让你躺很久还睡不着。\n  5. 睡前洗个热水澡\n  能让身体放松下来，入睡速度更快。\n  6. 脑子停不下来就写下来\n  把烦心事和待办清单写下，大脑会更容易放松。\n  7. 固定上床时间\n  每天差不多时间睡，生物钟会越来越稳定。\n  8. 试试深呼吸放松法\n  吸气4秒，停4秒，呼气6秒，慢慢就有困意了。\n  收藏这组，今晚试试看\nConstraints: 3:4 vertical aspect ratio, 3 columns × 3 rows grid with visible dividers, all Chinese text legible at mobile viewing distance, each panel must work as standalone image after cropping, no text crossing panel boundaries\nAvoid: cheap marketing aesthetic, over-decoration, illegible small text, chaotic color mixing, text overlapping grid lines",
