焰与勇敢，黄色为祖先与丰收；核心特征总结：尚黑贵左、银饰繁复、百褶层叠、刺绣精美\\nConstraints: all text must be simplified Chinese, clear and legible at reading distance; layout must follow the five-zone structure exactly; museum-quality realism without poster or commercial aesthetics; accurate ethnic costume structure; professional exhibition panel proportions\\nAvoid: poster aesthetic, studio photography look, e-commerce product page styling, anime or illustration style, cosplay appearance, incorrect structural labels, blurry or garbled text, English or pinyin, fake materials, excessive decoration, Instagram-friendly filters, romanticized fantasy styling\",\"size\":\"1536x1024\",\"quality\":\"medium\",\"n\":1,\"output_format\":\"png\"}",
