rict 3x3 grid, consistent character likeness of Zhao Ling'er across all panels, torn paper framing device identical in each panel, outfit colors must match specified palette\\nAvoid: harsh shadows, photorealistic rendering, inconsistent character proportions between panels, busy backgrounds that compete with the character expressions\",\"size\":\"1024x1024\",\"quality\":\"medium\",\"n\":1,\"output_format\":\"png\"}",
