        "prompt": "Create an editorial photo of Korean café-style coffee and pastries, shot on a smartphone for Instagram.\n\nStyle/medium: smartphone photography, Instagram aesthetic, flat lay and angled shots, photorealistic\nComposition: overhead flat lay and 45-degree angle shots, natural framing, casual smartphone framing\nSubject: Korean café latte art, iced coffee, croissants, tiramisu, macarons, minimalist ceramic plates, marble table surface\nScene/backdrop: bright Korean café interior, wooden tables, soft natural window light, clean minimalist aesthetic\nLighting/mood: soft natural daylight from large windows, bright and airy, cozy and inviting\nColor palette: warm browns and creams from coffee and pastries, soft whites, muted pastels, natural wood tones\nMaterials/textures: glossy ceramic cups, flaky pastry layers, smooth latte foam, marble grain, matte wooden surfaces\nText (verbatim): \"【描写规则】\\n・像用白色笔画出那样的细手绘线条\\n・一笔写成风格的粗糙、略微不均匀\\n・像描摹物体外周那样添加轮廓线\\n・用箭头或虚线制造视线引导\\n【文本规则】\\n・日语手写文字（平假名7成、简单汉字3成）\\n・简短，像自言自语一样的评论\\n・语气是\"日记・一言・情感寄托\"\\n【评论生成规则】\\n・饮料 → 味道・温度・心情（例：清爽、温柔的甜味）\\n・食物 → 口感・美味（例：湿润、最高）\\n・空间 → 氛围（例：放松、美好时光）\\n・整体 → 一言总结（例：幸福过头了～）\\n【装饰】\\n・蒸汽、闪闪发光、心形、小表情符号等适度添加\\n・不过度，留出\"空白\"\\n【完成风格】\\n・Instagram故事风、杂志的粗糙笔记风   ・时尚且轻松的氛围\"\nConstraints: no people in frame; handwritten annotation style overlay with thin white sketch lines, rough single-stroke style, outline tracing around objects, arrows and dotted lines for visual guidance; Japanese handwritten text (70% hiragana, 30% simple kanji), short diary-like comments; decorative elements: steam, sparkles, hearts, small emoticons used sparingly with intentional white space; Instagram story style, magazine rough notes aesthetic, fashionable and relaxed mood\nAvoid: stock photo look, overly polished commercial photography, cluttered composition, heavy filters, watermark, 8K stuffer words",
